<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

	<PropertyGroup>
		<TargetFramework>net10.0</TargetFramework>
		<ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
		<Nullable>enable</Nullable>
		<Version>4.9.2-rc.30</Version>
		<PackageReleaseNotes>v4.9.2-rc.30: P2PDispatcher per-attempt budget bumped from 30s to 60s (cumulative `DispatchTimeoutMs * MaxRetries` from 90s to 180s). The 30s default was too tight for two real-world cases the rc.28+/rc.29 SCTP backpressure fixes exposed: (1) >1MB result push-back at ~1.5 MB/s SCTP throughput hits 30s after just ~45MB; (2) 10-way concurrent dispatch contends per-peer message queues, so 5+ dispatches per peer serialize and accumulate compute+transfer latency past 30s. Diagnosed against `MultiPeer_Concurrent_10_DispatchedOverRealWebRtc_BitExact`: 3-attempt failure exactly at 4:52 (3 * 90s + setup), every attempt timed out at 90s. New default covers MultiPeer + LargeBuffer_10MB; LargeBuffer_100MB Stress test still needs custom override (~250s budget for 100MB push-back). Also documents the misleading semantics of MaxRetries — peer-loss retries (HandlePeerLost) fire only when a peer disconnects mid-dispatch; the multiplier just expands the result-wait budget. No API breakage; consumers can still override `dispatcher.DispatchTimeoutMs` and `dispatcher.MaxRetries` per swarm.</PackageReleaseNotes>
		<GeneratePackageOnBuild>True</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
		<GenerateDocumentationFile>true</GenerateDocumentationFile>
		<EmbedAllSources>true</EmbedAllSources>
		<DebugType>Embedded</DebugType>
		<Title>SpawnDev.ILGPU.P2P</Title>
		<Authors>LostBeard</Authors>
		<Description>P2P distributed GPU compute via SpawnDev.WebTorrent. AcceleratorType.P2P — the 7th ILGPU backend. Distributes kernels across connected devices via WebRTC. Scan a QR code, contribute GPU power.</Description>
		<PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/LostBeard/SpawnDev.ILGPU</PackageProjectUrl>
		<PackageLicenseFile>LICENSE.txt</PackageLicenseFile>
		<RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/LostBeard/SpawnDev.ILGPU.git</RepositoryUrl>
		<RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
		<PackageTags>P2P;WebRTC;WebTorrent;ILGPU;GPU;DistributedCompute;GPGPU</PackageTags>
		<LangVersion>latest</LangVersion>
		<AllowUnsafeBlocks>true</AllowUnsafeBlocks>
	</PropertyGroup>

	<ItemGroup>
		<None Include="..\LICENSE.txt" Pack="true" PackagePath="\" />
	</ItemGroup>

	<ItemGroup>
		<ProjectReference Include="..\SpawnDev.ILGPU\SpawnDev.ILGPU.csproj" />
		<PackageReference Include="SpawnDev.WebTorrent" Version="3.2.2-rc.3" />
	</ItemGroup>

</Project>
